HVQM 'aTh-DBUrY YHVNDB BN-UrKB 'aShUr-TShVH 'aTh-BNYV LBLThY ShThVTh-YYN VL'a ShThV 'yD-HYVM HZH KY ShM'yV 'aTh MTShVTh 'aBYHM V'aNKY DBUrThY 'aLYKM HShKM VDBUr VL'a ShM'yThM 'aLY.
