KY HQYMV BNY YHVNDB BN-UrKB 'aTh-MTShVTh 'aBYHM 'aShUr TShVM VH'yM HZH L'a ShM'yV 'aLY.
LKN KH-'aMUr YHVH 'aLHY TShB'aVTh 'aLHY YShUr'aL HNNY MBY'a 'aL-YHVDH V'aL KL-YVShBY YUrVShLM 'aTh KL-HUr'yH 'aShUr DBUrThY 'yLYHM Y'yN DBUrThY 'aLYHM VL'a ShM'yV V'aQUr'a LHM VL'a 'yNV.
VLBYTh HUrKBYM 'aMUr YUrMYHV KH-'aMUr YHVH TShB'aVTh 'aLHY YShUr'aL Y'yN 'aShUr ShM'yThM 'yL-MTShVTh YHVNDB 'aBYKM VThShMUrV 'aTh-KL-MTShVThYV VTh'yShV KKL 'aShUr- TShVH 'aThKM.
